        <h2>House Sparrow</h2>
        <p>The House Sparrow is a small, social bird often seen in gardens across New Zealand. They feed on seeds and insects and are frequent visitors to bird feeders. Their chirping and playful flitting make them a familiar and lively garden presence.</p>

